the birds are perched in a tree-margin infront of my window. -- here i upload as first 3 soundscapes ....the first 4 1/2 hours 

... herein is to hear a  kitchen exhaust pipe beneath my window with its sound .. and also our daily food-suplyment with truck and car at our kitchen in this back-house garden.

at around highnoon till 13,00 p.m. i made a short walk in my nearer residential-living area. -- these some cuts are recorded with my live comments of the recording situation. -- back home then in my attic-living-room i did again short some cuts from my window to the tree-line in our backhouse-garden.
